###  http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#FunctionalSubstance
<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#FunctionalSubstance> rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Substance> .


