<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#InformationRealization> rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#InformationEntity> .


###  http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#LocalConcept
<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#LocalConcept> rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Concept> .


