<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Method> rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Description> .


###  http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Narrative
