<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#NaturalPerson> rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Person> ,
                                                                                      <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#PhysicalAgent> .


###  http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Norm
<http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Norm> rdfs:subClassOf <http://www.ontologydesignpatterns.org/ont/dul/DUL.owl#Description> .


